# Canonical Sepolia RPC. packages/chain/sepolia.ts resolves it in this order:
# SEPOLIA_RPC env -> RPC env -> macOS Keychain (honeycomb_sepolia_rpc) -> public node.
# On Luke's mac the Goldsky secret comes from Keychain; leave this unset there.
# Set it explicitly on CI / non-mac, e.g.:
# SEPOLIA_RPC=https://edge.goldsky.com/standard/evm/11155111?secret=<YOUR_GOLDSKY_SECRET>

# Sepolia signer for create_bounty (broadcasts a real tx). Read-only tools work
# without it. On Luke's mac run-with-secrets.sh loads it from the keychain.
# keychain service: honeycomb_sep_private_key
# SEP_PRIVATE_KEY=

# Chainlink Confidential AI Attester key for grade_submission's validity half.
# Without it the execution score still computes; the validity call throws.
# keychain service: honeycomb_inference_api_key
# INFERENCE_API_KEY_VAR=

# --- optional overrides (sane defaults in chain.ts / the tools) ---
# HONEYCOMB_PYTHON=        # python with google-cloud-bigquery for query_reputation
# HONEYCOMB_GRADER_VENV=   # bin/ of the grader venv (demeter) for grade_submission
